# {{ name }} (Python app)

Minimal Python app scaffold using uv and Buck2 macros (`nix_python_binary`).

Quickstart:
- Edit `pyproject.toml` to set metadata and dependencies (PEP 621; hatchling backend).
- Generate a lockfile with uv:
  - `uv lock` (base)
  - Optionally include groups (dev/test) when enabled later: `uv lock --group dev --group test`
- Build with Buck2 once glue is generated per repo docs.


